title: Trailer Wiring Installation: CURT 56214 on 2013 Chevrolet Cruze
description:
This video depicts the installation of the CURT 56214 custom vehicle-to-trailer wiring harness on the 2013 Chevrolet Cruze. You must read and understand the supplied instruction sheet(s) prior to installing. 


Instruction Sheet:
https://www.curtmfg.com/masterlibrary/56214/installsheet/CME_56214_INS.PDF


Application Coverage:
2011- 2016 Chevrolet Cruze (Except Diesel Models)


Warning:
-This video is intended to be used as reference. Please refer to print instructions for complete installation information.
